description.en-us: Hot Tunerz (also called "Car Tunerz") are vehicles inspired by the tuner scene of 2000s, in a cartoonish theme. They are similar to the 'Tooned series of cars, some castings were reused for that series. They were released in both 1:55 scale and 1:20 scale. This series was designed by Eric Tscherne .
